_json.description: #throwbackthursday November 2014 --> December 2018 Sometimes I like to take a stroll down memory lane to revisit (1.) how terrible my eyebrows were and (2.) how terrible quality hair dye and heat styling ruined my hair in college. The first pic was my natural texture back then! I have very few pictures without my hair straightened or curled back then, but I cringe at every picture where I left it natural because it's just sad to see how unhealthy it was!
